  resolution-by: phase-4
  proposal: weekly Apalache check on specs/tla/WorkloadIdentityFederation.tla

@open-question Q2 "Workforce Identity Federation (Google Workspace SSO via FerrisKey)"
  resolution-by: future-pass
  proposal: SC-IAM-010 deferred to v2; v1 stays internal-facing

@open-question Q3 "Kanidm sidecar fallback if FerrisKey ES256 + WebAuthn lag"
  resolution-by: phase-3
  proposal: ES256 + WebAuthn must land in vendored fork; revisit only on miss

@open-question Q4 "Multi-region failover (eu-north-1 outage)"
  resolution-by: future-pass
  proposal: GCP IAM allow-policy can cite a second WIF pool in eu-west-1
